        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". The names coincide so far as Zadok; but either Meraioth and Ahitub have been transposed (see ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1Chronicles 6:7",
        "children": []
